      <title>KBW 称，德国商业银行股价有望因 UniCredit 交易上涨 35%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/commerzbank-shares-seen-rising-35-on-unicredit-deal-kbw-says</link>
