      <title>印度债券遭遇指数加入以来最大资金流出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/indian-bonds-see-biggest-outflows-since-jpmorgan-index-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国债券收益率上升削弱了印度固定收益证券的吸引力，海外投资者正在以至少 6 月以来最快的速度削减印度债券的持有量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/indian-bonds-see-biggest-outflows-since-jpmorgan-index-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 04:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市涨跌互现，交易员考虑特朗普的选择和利率：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周的下跌抹去了唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选以来的大部分股市涨幅，随后股市出现小幅波动，交易员们期待着经济增长和利率走势方面的新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税担忧加剧 新兴市场债券或将遭遇损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/emerging-bonds-look-primed-for-losses-as-trump-tariff-fears-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者抛售降息押注、对关税贸易战的担忧加剧以及美元飙升，新兴市场本币债券的前景正在恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/emerging-bonds-look-primed-for-losses-as-trump-tariff-fears-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
